high_descs: Move to the kitchen table, standing behind the chair.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and slice the food on the shelf.
Move to stand in front the stove, still carrying the knife.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Move back to the fridge.
Remove slices of food from the shelf.
Carry the sliced food to the microwave.
Place the sliced food in the microwave, cook it, and then remove it.
Carry the cooked food to the kitchen table.
Place the food on the table next to the plant.
anns.task_desc: Move cooked food to the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn around to face the dining table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Go to the refrigerator.
Open and then close the refrigerator.
Go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the refrigerator.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go back to the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave, start it, and then remove the bread.
Go to the dining table
Place the bread on the table between the potted plant and the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a knife with a piece of bread then put the bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn left to the round table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is in between the spatulas.
Turn right and go in front of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, cut the bread on the refrigerator's second shelf, close the refrigerator
Turn around, go in front of the oven.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go in front of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, take a piece of bread from the second shelf, close the refrigerator.
Turn around, go in front of the oven.
Put the bread in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the bread from the microwave.
Turn right, go to the round table, go to the chair in the corner of the room near the round table.
Put the bread on the round table near the plant and spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of microwaved bread on the round table.
